column.name: resource_ids
column.Comment: 资源ID集合,多个资源时用逗号(,)分隔

column.name: scope
column.Comment: 客户端申请的权限范围

column.name: authorities
column.Comment: 客户端所拥有的Spring Security的权限值，多个用逗号(,)分隔

column.name: access_token_validity
column.Comment: 访问令牌有效时间值(单位:秒)

column.name: refresh_token_validity
column.Comment: 更新令牌有效时间值(单位:秒)

column.name: token
column.Comment: OAuth2AccessToken.java对象序列化后的二进制数据

column.name: authentication
column.Comment: AuthorizationRequestHolder.java对象序列化后的二进制数据

column.name: token
column.Comment: OAuth2RefreshToken.java对象序列化后的二进制数据

column.name: authentication
column.Comment: OAuth2Authentication.java对象序列化后的二进制数据

column.name: limit_submit_time
column.Comment: 限时提交时间(...分钟内不允许提交)

column.name: limit_enter_time
column.Comment: 限时进入时间(....分钟后不允许参加考试)

column.name: enable_monitor
column.Comment: 是否开启抓拍监控(0:关闭1:开启)

column.name: limit_screen_count
column.Comment: 识别到屏幕异常...次,强制收卷

column.name: allow_redo
column.Comment: 考试截止日前运行重做....次

column.name: allow_check_score
column.Comment: 允许学生查看分数(0:不允许1:允许)

column.name: allow_multidevice
column.Comment: 允许多终端考试(0:网页考试,1:app考试2:允许网页与app考试)

column.name: num_over_count
column.Comment: 检测到考生人数大于1人次数

column.name: before_exam_img
column.Comment: 考前人脸拍照照片(OSS存储)

column.name: paper_type
column.Comment: 试卷类型( 1固定试卷 2临时试卷 3班级试卷 4.时段试卷 5.推送试卷)

column.name: limit_start_time
column.Comment: 时段试卷 开始时间

column.name: limit_end_time
column.Comment: 时段试卷 结束时间

column.name: paper_type
column.Comment: 试卷类型( 1固定试卷 2临时试卷 3班级试卷 4.时段试卷 )

column.name: is_publish
column.Comment: 考试是否发放[0未发放,1发放]

column.name: question_type
column.Comment: 1.单选题 2.多选题 3.判断题 4.填空题 5.简答题

column.name: info_text_content_id
column.Comment: 题目 填空、 题干、解析、答案等信息

column.name: is_lock
column.Comment: 题库锁定,不允许查看[1锁定,0未锁定]

column.name: is_pass
column.Comment: 题库审批情况[0不通过,1通过]

column.name: name
column.Comment: 语文 数学 英语 等

column.name: level
column.Comment: 年级 (1-12) 小学 初中 高中 大学

column.name: password
column.Comment: 用户密码（可以为空，支持只用验证码注册、登录）

column.name: status
column.Comment: 用户状态：1能登录，0不能登录
